  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  children in the clinical or borderline range of the EB scale (cut-off = 21 or higher)
             of the Child Behavior Checklist preschool form (Achenbach &amp; Rescorla, 2000a)

          -  three to six years old and still in kindergarten at the beginning of the intervention

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  children with intellectual disabilities (average IQ &lt; 5.5)

          -  highly gifted children (average IQ &gt;14.5)
      </textblock>
